h the natural gas industry is paying to support the efforts to shut down Indian Point? Even though it may sound counterintuitive to engineering types, many businesses are run based on Sun Tzu's dictum that &quot;The enemy of my enemy is my friend.&quot; When nuclear reactors are shut down, both prices and unit volume increase for the fossil fuels that replace the lost power.<br>
<br>
